<div class="jiaruwm_tit"><span></span>法务主管/经理</div>
<div><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作地点：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">北京</span><span style="font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作性质：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">全职</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">招聘人数：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">1人</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">职位类别：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://jobs.zhaopin.com/beijing/sj225/" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: none;">法务经理/主管</a></span></span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">岗位职责：</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">1. 合同制定：公司合同、规定、制度的制定、撰写等，对合同进行法律审核，提出修改意见；完善合同管理制度，对归档合同进行登记、编号及存放；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">2. 为相关部门的业务活动提供法律咨询，草拟公司对外的法律函件，对可能出现的法律风险出具法律意见；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">3. 参与重大经营决策的法律论证，对公司员工进行法律培训；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">4. 公司常规性法律风险的预防、规避和管理</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">5. 协助解决各类纠纷；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">6. 代表公司处理一些诉讼或非诉讼法律事务，维护公司合法权益；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">7.&nbsp;与外协律师事务所沟通，处理公司与合作单位的相关法律事务。</span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">任职要求：</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">1、具有本科及以上学历，法学相关专业毕业；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">2、具有2-5年以上的法律相关工作经验；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">3、通过国家司法考试；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">4、为人正直、品行端正，具有敬业精神和团队精神，具备将强的沟通能力、协调能力、执行能力。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">有意向者请发送简历至邮箱571988202#qq.com（发送时请将#改为@）</span></p><p><span style="display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://jobs.zhaopin.com/beijing/sj225/" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: none;"></a></span><br></p><p><br></p></div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="jiaruwm_tit"><span></span>证券分析师（偏研究方向）</div>
<div><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作地点：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">北京</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作性质：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">全职</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">招聘人数：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">1人</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">职位类别：</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">证券分析/金融研究</span></span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">岗位职责：<br>1、负责每日股票市场投资分析与资讯发布，包括市场，热点，新闻，股票池等。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">2、负责股票特征以及投资策略进行研究和分析；<br>3、负责根据宏观经济，深入剖析解读国内外值得关注的政策信息和经济动态，预判市场趋势，提供热点分析及投资策略分析，并据此撰写日策略、周策略等研究报告；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">4、建立相关数据资料及模型，撰写市场分析报告，完成相关研究课题，对业务提供策略支持。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"></span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">任职要求：</span><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">1、研究生及以上学历，经验丰富的本科学历者可考虑；金融、证券、经济等相关专业背景；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">2、具备较强的信息收集、热点捕捉和文字写作能力，以及独立的行情研究与判断的能力；<br>3、熟练掌握证券投资分析方法，能够撰写证券投资分析报告，挖掘具有投资机会的行业及个股；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">4、掌握各类经济分析理论和工具，对金融市场规律有深刻理解，对宏观经济层面有独到的分析能力；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';">5、有证券咨询从业资格或通过相关考试，有本行业工作经验者，优先考虑。</span></p><p><br></p></div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="jiaruwm_tit"><span></span>证券分析师（偏交易方向）</div>
<div><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作地点：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">北京</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">工作性质：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">全职</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">招聘人数：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">1人</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block;">职位类别：</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px; display: inline-block; width: 180px; word-wrap: break-word;">证券分析/金融研究</span></span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">岗位职责：</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">1、深谙证券市场，精通大盘与股票分析，对宏观经济形势有成熟的认识与见解；<br>2、专业能力强，有自己独特的投资理念与风格，具备一定的研发能力。能构建自己的投资组合产品，并根据客户的投资理财需求，提供具体的可持续解决方案；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">3、根据公司制定的投资策略以及风险控制要求，严格执行交易思路，独立完成指令权限范围内的证券交易，并对每日仓位明细、资产配置进行总结；<br>4、团队协作能力强，能将团队相关研究成果及时吸收、转化。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"></span></p><hr><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">职位要求：<br>1、研究生及以上学历，经验丰富的本科学历者可考虑；金融、证券、经济等相关专业背景；&nbsp;</span><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">2、分析能力强，在金融投资等领域具有投资实践经验，提供投资成果者优先；<br>3、具有很强的工作责任心和团队合作精神，具备较强的抗压能力；</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">4、有证券咨询从业资格或通过相关考试，有本行业工作经验者，优先考虑。</span></p><p><br></p></div>
</li>
